  "note": "Standards mappings are relevant, not prescriptive. A finding is not a compliance verdict; these references locate a finding in the external landscape so a Builder, a Guardian, and an auditor can read the same result. EU AI Act articles apply only where the deployer's system is high-risk under the Act and are transparency/oversight references, never asserted violations.",
